OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FA prisoner who stabbed Lostprophets
OL,7,Ffrontman Ian Watkins to death said he
OL,8,Ftold the singer "this is what
OL,9,Fpaedophiles deserve" before the
OL,10,Fattack, a court has heard.
OL,12,FWatkins, who was 48, was stabbed in
OL,13,Fhis cell at high-security HMP
OL,14,FWakefield on 11 October last year.
OL,16,FFellow prisoners Rico Gedel and Samuel
OL,17,FDodsworth are on trial at Leeds Crown
OL,18,FCourt accused of his murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
