PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FGiving evidence on Wednesday, Gedel,
OL,7,F25, told the court he hated sharing a
OL,8,Fwing with sex offenders and had openly
OL,9,Fthreatened to assault "any number of
OL,10,Fpaedophiles" if he was not transferred.
OL,12,FHe said he had decided to stab someone
OL,13,Fin order to get moved off the wing,
OL,14,Fand chose Watkins, who was in the cell
OL,15,Fnext to him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FGedel, who is already serving a life
OL,7,Fsentence for murder, said he felt he
OL,8,Fhad been set up by prison officers who
OL,9,Fknew how much he hated paedophiles,
OL,10,Fand said they were "just as much to
OL,11,Fblame as I am".
OL,13,FJurors heard he had a hatred of sex
OL,14,Foffenders because he had family
OL,15,Fmembers who had been sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted, adding: "The reason I feel
OL,17,Fso disgusted about sexual assault is -
OL,18,FIt's not something you can take away."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FGedel said he made a point of finding
OL,7,Fout who the sex offenders were on his
OL,8,Fwing when he was moved to HMP
OL,9,FWakefield.
OL,11,FHe said he was moved back onto the
OL,12,Fsame wing as Watkins the night before
OL,13,Fthe fatal attack after he assaulted
OL,14,Fthree prisoners on another wing,
OL,15,Fclaiming one of them was "selling baby
OL,16,Fphotos and boasting about him being a
OL,17,Fpaedophile".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FThe night he was moved, he told the
OL,7,Fcourt he heard the inmate next door
OL,8,Ftelling a prison officer he "needed a
OL,9,Fphoto printed off of a female" and
OL,10,Ffound out that it was Watkins.
OL,12,FGedel then started verbally abusing
OL,13,Fhim through the cell walls, and said
OL,14,FWatkins had used racial slurs to him.
OL,16,FThe next morning he was given the
OL,17,Fmakeshift knife used in the attack by
OL,18,FDodsworth after telling him that he
OL,19,Fneeded a weapon.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,F"There was no other option than to
OL,7,Fcause violence to get off the wing,"
OL,8,FGedel added.
OL,10,FHe said that he told Watkins: "This is
OL,11,Fwhat paedophiles deserve."
OL,13,FGedel admitted to the attack and told
OL,14,Fthe court he was not in court to prove
OL,15,Fhis innocence.
OL,17,F"I'm not here to prove my innocence, I
OL,18,Fadmit to what's happened, whether that
OL,19,Fwas the intention or not, I take full
OL,20,Fresponsibility for what's happened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,F"My heart was saying 'he deserves it,
OL,7,Fhe's a paedophile. Think of your
OL,8,Ffamily members, think of his victims'.
OL,9,FMy brain was saying 'it's not the
OL,10,Fthing to do'."
OL,12,FAsked by his barrister Peter Moulson
OL,13,FKC if he wanted to kill Watkins, Gedel
OL,14,Fsaid: "Some part of me did, yes."
OL,16,FGedel, who was initially referred to
OL,17,Fby police as Rashid Gedel, and 44-year-
OL,18,Fold Dodsworth both deny murder and
OL,19,Fpossession of a makeshift knife in
OL,20,Fprison.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
