PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778854269
OL,3,CPrison killer told Ian Watkins 'this
OL,4,Cis what paedophiles deserve'
OL,6,FWatkins was jailed for 29 years in
OL,7,FDecember 2013, with a further six
OL,8,Fyears on licence, after admitting a
OL,9,Fstring of sex offences - including the
OL,10,Fattempted rape of a fan's baby.
OL,12,FThe trial continues.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
